lly have the time or even will to do anything but <strong>create</strong> and improve them.</p><p>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in and it all looks great, that\'s <strong>development.</strong></p><p>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually in it....</p><p>So I create an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</p><p>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain them, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this whole thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Chances are your situation is not quite as elaborate, but this is the secret to your success and what we do in a nutshell. The only difference is we do this all online, which is called <strong>web development and marketing</strong>.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>So you want to take your business to the next level?  I\'ve been there!  It\'s not going to be easy, but we have the three phase plan that has worked for others in your situation.  Knowing you are headed in the right direction will make it easier.</p><p>First things first. We will assess your current marketing plan. Suggest tweaks or additions that</p><p>We can not wait to sit down and guide you through the process.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>In th