able Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain them, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this whole thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Chances are your situation is not quite as elaborate, but this is the secret to your success and what we do in a nutshell. The only difference is we do this all online, which is called <strong>web development and marketing</strong>.</p><p> </p><p>For your platform to work beyond a hobby based business, scalability is key. That means you need a team to get you to the next level....</p><p> </p><p>...And this team has a plan.  A plan that has worked for others EXACTLY in your situation.  It\'s not going to be easy, but knowing you are headed in the right direction will make it doable and you might even make some friends along the way.</p><p>So about that plan...</p><p>When you send in your Expansion Idea it gets uploaded to a flash drive in Tibet where all of our most spiritual monk advisers meditate to check basic viability of that idea in this market.  Chakras are performed.  Auras can flare. If the idea marinades in Earth\'s ether with enough energy to compel a white dove to soar from Tibet to New York while carrying that flash drive then the idea was meant to be.  Suggested tweaks or additions will come in the form of intuition which we will communicate to you upon visiting for tea. Namaste.</p><p> </p><p>But enough about the process. We will walk you through it step by step anyway. I\'m excited.  Who doesn\'t get excited about new opportunity!?</p><p> </p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"be8e3446-071d-4667-9368-945b8158bc49\";s:5:\"style\";a:6:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:10:\"font_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";}}}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Articles on Front end development and Content Marketing\";s:4:\"text\";s:158:\"<p>Front end development</p><p> </p><p>Content advertising</p><p>A custom plan to target your audience usingn what ever stream of information they trust.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:4;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:4;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"d126a64f-3679-4199-8440-44206b01ea05\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#777777\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#777777\";}}}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:40:\"\"We Believe the Best Company Should Win\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:716:\"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">If you are ready to take on more clientele, then it is time for you to get an affordable professionally created and managed online presence. We are the team to do that.  We are a team of maverick free-lancers. This means you are paying virtually no overhead and you are getting treated as more than just a number.  Don\'t go the corporate route especially if it is your first time.  Among freelancers we are the most affordable, but we demand flexibility.  This is the trade-off.  Again, we promise we won\'t quote you a price unless it is a win-win for both of us.  Our goal is to earn 