really have the time or even will to do anything but <strong>create</strong> and improve them.</p><p>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in and it all looks great, that\'s <strong>development.</strong></p><p>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually in it....</p><p>So I create an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</p><p>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain them, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this whole thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Chances are your situation is not quite as elaborate, but this is the secret to your success and what we do in a nutshell. The only difference is we do this all online, which is called <strong>web development and marketing</strong>.</p><p> </p><p>For your platform to work beyond a hobby based business, scalability is key. That means you need a team to get you to the next level....</p><p> </p><p>...And this team has a plan.  A plan that has worked for others EXACTLY in your situation.  It\'s not going to be easy, but knowing you are headed in the right direction will make it doable and you might even make some friends along the way.</p><p>So about that plan...</p><p>When you send in your Expansion Idea it gets uploaded to a flash drive in Tibet where all of our most spiritual monk advisers meditate to check basic viability of that idea in this market.  Chakras are performed.  Auras can flare. If the idea marinades in Earth\'s ether with enough energy to compel a white dove to soar from Tibet to New York while carrying that flash drive then the idea was meant to be.  Suggested tweaks or additions will come in the form of intuition which we will communicate to you upon visiting for tea. Namaste.</p><p> </p><p>But enough about the process. We will walk you through it step by step anyway. I\'m excited.  Who doesn\'t get excited about new opportunity!?</p><p> </p><p>Also, the universe is telling me that by getting our <strong>monthly newsletter</strong> you will become fully enlightened and reach nirvana... as long as your nirvana is growing your business. Namaste.</p><p> </p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"be8e3446-071d-4667-9368-945b8158bc49\";s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:10:\"font_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";}}}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Articles on Front end development and Content Marketing\";s:4:\"text\";s:158:\"<p>Front end development</p><p> </p><p>Content advertising</p><p>A custom plan to target your audience usingn what ever stream of information they trust.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:4;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:4;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"d126a64f-3679-4199-8440-44206b01ea05\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color