"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:2;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"action_text\";s:90:\"<h3>Schedule a 1 on 1 Call Today So That We Can Expand Your Online Presence Tomorrow!</h3>\";s:15:\"action_btn_link\";s:7:\"#pg-8-9\";s:15:\"action_btn_text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:6:\"inline\";b:1;s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:13:\"Sydney_Action\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:2;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"1a6b891a-1da4-4814-99e0-980d4e96ff24\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#443f3f\";}}}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"The Secret Behind Your Success\";s:4:\"text\";s:3819:\"<p>Lets start off by saying we are both remarkable at what we do. But being remarkable has not been enough, has it?  So we must combine forces.  </p><p>Its quite simple you make content, I put it in front of the right peoples smiling faces, and we both reap the benefits, right?</p><p>See for your platform to work beyond a hobby based business, scalability is key. That means you need a team to get you to the next level....</p><p>... and my team has mastered The Three Phase Growth Plan.  It is the same plan that has worked for others that are EXACTLY in your situation.  It\'s not going to be easy, but knowing you are headed in the right direction will make all the difference and you might even make some friends along the way.</p><p>But before that plan even goes into motion something even more powerful graces it with its energies...</p><p>Get this!  When you send in your Expansion Idea it gets uploaded to a flash drive in Tibet where a monastery full of the most spiritual monks meditate to check basic viability of that idea in this market.  Chakras are performed.  Auras can flare. And if the idea marinades in Earth\'s ether just right and with enough energy to compel a white dove to soar from Tibet to New York whilst carrying that flash drive, then the idea was meant to be.  Suggested tweaks or additions will come in the form of intuition which we will communicate to you upon visiting for tea. Namaste.</p><p> </p><p>But enough about the initial process. What happens after that?</p><p> </p><p>Well, here is one way to think about the happenings:</p><p>Imagine your new Frankenstein Cyborg Baby <strong>creation</strong> is ready and it is just great.  You just know that they are gonna be the newest and coolest, and totally replace robot butlers forever.  But you are stuck selling them to a few people out of your garage which doesn\'t work well and brings you away from the fun part, like coming up with a better design for its fully reticulating neck and programming it to collect cobwebs off the ceiling.</p><p>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in making it all look very professional. Well call that <strong>development.</strong></p><p>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually going into it....</p><p>So here is where it gets interesting.  I plan an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</p><p>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and make them happier, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this entire thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p><strong>This is the secret to your success</strong> and what we do in a nutshell!!  The only difference is we do this all online, so it is called <strong>WEB development and marketing.</strong></p><p>So there is the secret!</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Also, the universe is telling me that by getting our <strong>monthly newsletter</strong> you will become fully enlightened and reach nirvana... as long as your nirvana is growing your business. Namaste.</p><p> </p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:3;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"be8e3446-071d-4667-9368-945b8158bc49\";s:5:\"style\";a:5:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:10:\"font_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";}}}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Articles on Front end development and Content Marketing\";s:4:\"text\";s:158:\"<p>Front end development</p><p> </p><p>Content advertising</p><p>A custom plan to target your audience usingn what ever stream of information they trust.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:4;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:4;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"d126a64f-3679-4199-8440-44206b01ea05\";s:5:\"style\";a:4:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";s:17:\"content_alignment\";s:4:\"left\";s:11:\"title_color\";s:7:\"#777777\";s:14:\"headings_color\";s:7:\"#777777\";}}}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:5:\"title\";s:40:\"\"We Believe the Best Company Should Win\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:716:\"<h3 style=\"tex